{"word":"G428 - ἀνεύθετος - aneúthetos - an-yoo'-the-tos - Not commodious","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀνεύθετος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">aneúthetos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">an-yoo'-the-tos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Not commodious</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"வசதியில்லாத - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"not convenient, not commodious, not fit"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and <a href=\"#/G2111 - εὔθετος - eúthetos - yoo'-thet-os/2111\">G2111</a>; <i>not well set</i>, that is, <i>inconvenient:</i> - not commodious.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}